      <title>“很棒的协议”：特鲁多的保守党对手向特朗普推销能源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/canada-s-pierre-poilievre-tells-jordan-peterson-he-s-got-great-deal-for-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自赢得美国大选以来，唐纳德·特朗普一直嘲讽加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多，称他为美国第51个州的州长，威胁征收25%的关税，并发泄美国因贸易逆差而被北方邻国欺骗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/canada-s-pierre-poilievre-tells-jordan-peterson-he-s-got-great-deal-for-trump</guid>
